quote.summary: Jinke Smart Services Group Co Ltd is a China-based company principally engaged in the provision of property management services. The Company mainly operates four businesses. The space property management services business mainly includes property management services and value-added services to non-property owners. The local catering services business mainly provides services to property owners and clients, including catering services, hotel management services, and catering supply chain services. The community value-added services business mainly provides services to property owners, residents and large property owners, including home-living services, community management services, home-decoration services, and asset operation services. The smart living technology solutions business mainly provides digital and intelligent technology solutions, including intelligent design services, smart sales assistance services, and smart integrated operation platform services.
